       !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:7e81cc55bfaa7140318103e270fb5e41e7ee0ab5c82d8ce7ae587f6586adafa0\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nStock Inventory Valuation Report is the report that display value of all products in internal location.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use this module, you need to:\n\n1. Go to Inventory > Reporting > Inventory Valuation.\n2. Select Inventory At Date.\n3. You can now choose a few additional options: \"View report\", \"Export PDF\" and \"Export XLSX\".\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/stock-logistics-reporting/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/stock-logistics-reporting/issues/new?body=module:%20stock_inventory_valuation_report%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Ecosoft\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [Pimolnat Suntian](mailto:pimolnats@ecosoft.co.th)\n- [Ooops404](https://ooops404.com)\n  : - [Francesco Foresti](mailto:francesco.foresti@ooops404.com)\n- [Cetmix](https://cetmix.com)\n  : - [Andrey Solodovnikov](mailto:andrejsolodovnikov@gmail.com)\n- [PyTech SRL](https://www.pytech.it)\n  : - [Alessandro Uffreduzzi](mailto:alessandro.uffreduzzi@pytech.it)\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/stock-logistics-reporting](https://github.com/OCA/stock-logistics-reporting/tree/14.0/stock_inventory_valuation_report) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.stock_inventory_valuation_report.wizard.stock_quantity_history", "documentation": ["Copyright 2019 Ecosoft Co., Ltd. (http://ecosoft.co.th)", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.stock_inventory_valuation_report.wizard.stock_quantity_history._logger", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.stock_inventory_valuation_report.wizard.stock_quantity_history.StockQuantityHistory", "bases": ["models.TransientModel"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.stock_inventory_valuation_report.wizard.stock_quantity_history.StockQuantityHistory.button_export_html", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.stock_inventory_valuation_report.wizard.stock_quantity_history.StockQuantityHistory.button_export_pdf", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.stock_inventory_valuation_report.wizard.stock_quantity_history.StockQuantityHistory.button_export_xlsx", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.stock_inventory_valuation_report.wizard.stock_quantity_history.StockQuantityHistory._prepare_stock_inventory_valuation_report", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.stock_invento